data <- data %>%
  rename(RANK = RANG)
top.10_boys <- data %>%
  filter(GESCHLECHT == "m") %>%
  filter(RANK <= 10) %>%
  pull(VORNAME) %>%
  unique()

top.10_girls <- data %>%
  filter(GESCHLECHT == "w") %>%
  filter(RANK <= 10) %>%
  pull(VORNAME) %>%
  unique()


df.top.10_boys <- data %>%
  filter(GESCHLECHT == "m") %>%
  filter(VORNAME %in% top.10_boys) %>%
